-text-editor\" data-id=\"a33e68f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>La pr\u00e9carit\u00e9 \u00e9conomique des femmes n&rsquo;est pas une fatalit\u00e9, c&rsquo;est le r\u00e9sultat d&rsquo;in\u00e9galit\u00e9s structurelles qui se cumulent tout au long de la vie. La Fondation des Femmes agit concr\u00e8tement pour accompagner les femmes vers l&rsquo;autonomie financi\u00e8re, soutenir les associations de terrain qui luttent contre la pr\u00e9carit\u00e9, et porter des recommandations politiques pour transformer durablement la soci\u00e9t\u00e9.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1a5f6d8 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"1a5f6d8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"689\" src=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/hero-oeuvrer-1024x882.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-16079\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/hero-oeuvrer-1024x882.webp 1024w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/hero-oeuvrer-300x259.webp 300w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/hero-oeuvrer-768x662.webp 768w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/hero-oeuvrer.webp 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f2d1cf7 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"f2d1cf7\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t