llect\u00e9s dans  43 magasins redistribu\u00e9s  \u00e0 70 associations en 2024<\/div>\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-counter-number-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number-prefix\"><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number\" data-duration=\"2000\" data-to-value=\"322113\" data-from-value=\"0\" data-delimiter=\" \">0<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number-suffix\"><\/span>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-db122c1 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"db122c1\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-56caa06 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"56caa06\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>collecte automnale<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a513f5f elementor-widget elementor-widget-counter\" data-id=\"a513f5f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"counter.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-counter\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-counter-title\">produits collect\u00e9s dans  78 magasins redistribu\u00e9s  \u00e0 93 associations en 2024<\/div>\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-counter-number-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number-prefix\"><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number\" data-duration=\"2000\" data-to-value=\"432436\" data-from-value=\"0\" data-delimiter=\" \">0<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-counter-number-suffix\"><\/span>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d7cc421 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d7cc421\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Ces op\u00e9rations permettent de lutter concr\u00e8tement contre la pr\u00e9carit\u00e9 menstruelle et d&rsquo;am\u00e9liorer les conditions de vie des femmes les plus vuln\u00e9rables. En France, 1,7 million de femmes sont en situation de pr\u00e9carit\u00e9 menstruelle, c&rsquo;est-\u00e0-dire qu&rsquo;elles n&rsquo;ont pas les moyens d&rsquo;acheter des protections hygi\u00e9niques.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6b1fd02 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"6b1fd02\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ab9550e elementor-widget__width-initial text-pretty elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ab9550e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><span class=\"highlight-jaune\">Plaidoyer<\/span> <br>D\u00e9fendre l\u2019\u00e9mancipation \n\u00e9conomique des femmes<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-937c4c3 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"937c4c3\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b7f6766 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"b7f6766\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"585\" src=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/plaidoyer-defiscalisation.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-16081\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/plaidoyer-defiscalisation.webp 800w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/plaidoyer-defiscalisation-300x219.webp 300w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/plaidoyer-defiscalisation-768x562.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-725a458 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"725a458\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-41de0e7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"41de0e7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">D\u00e9fiscalisation des pensions alimentaires<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7c9e52b elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7c9e52b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>En 2025, la Fondation des Femmes s&rsquo;est mobilis\u00e9e, avec plusieurs associations partenaires, pour mettre fin \u00e0 une injustice fiscale touchant les familles monoparentales. Elle d\u00e9fend la d\u00e9fiscalisation des pensions alimentaires, rappelant que ces sommes ne constituent pas un revenu mais une contribution destin\u00e9e \u00e0 couvrir les besoins fondamentaux de l&rsquo;enfant.<br \/>Actuellement, les pensions alimentaires sont imposables pour le parent qui les re\u00e7oit \u2014 le plus souvent la m\u00e8re \u2014 et d\u00e9ductibles pour celui qui les verse. Ce syst\u00e8me p\u00e9nalise les m\u00e8res isol\u00e9es, qui sont 85% des parents isol\u00e9s en France, et renforce leur pr\u00e9carit\u00e9 \u00e9conomique.<br \/>Ce plaidoyer s&rsquo;inscrit dans le combat plus large de la Fondation pour l&rsquo;\u00e9mancipation \u00e9conomique des femmes et la lutte contre la pr\u00e9carit\u00e9 des m\u00e8res isol\u00e9es.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9ad8783 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"9ad8783\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-275ab23 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"275ab23\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7ed41a0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7ed41a0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">L\u2019Observatoire de l\u2019\u00e9mancipation \u00e9conomique des femmes<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a6ce135 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a6ce135\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Lanc\u00e9 en 2022 avec le soutien du Cr\u00e9dit Municipal de Paris, l&rsquo;Observatoire de l&rsquo;\u00e9mancipation \u00e9conomique des femmes r\u00e9unit des expertes pluridisciplinaires \u2014 \u00e9conomistes, historiennes, journalistes, sociologues \u2014 pour analyser les m\u00e9canismes de pr\u00e9carisation \u00e9conomique des femmes et formuler des recommandations politiques concr\u00e8tes.<br \/>Depuis 2022, l&rsquo;Observatoire a publi\u00e9 8 notes analysant le co\u00fbt \u00e9conomique que les femmes supportent \u00e0 diff\u00e9rentes \u00e9tapes de leur vie : le co\u00fbt de la justice pour les victimes de violences sexuelles, le co\u00fbt du divorce, le co\u00fbt d&rsquo;\u00eatre aidante, le co\u00fbt de la sniorit, le co\u00fbt d&rsquo;\u00eatre retrait\u00e9e. Ces travaux nourrissent les actions de plaidoyer de la Fondation et contribuent \u00e0 rendre visible une th\u00e9matique trop souvent absente du d\u00e9bat public.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-28cfb4e elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"28cfb4e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/observatoire-emancipation-economique-femmes\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">En savoir plus<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a9cdffd elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"a9cdffd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"585\" src=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/plaidoyer-observatoire-emancipation.webp\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-16082\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/plaidoyer-observatoire-emancipation.webp 800w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/plaidoyer-observatoire-emancipation-300x219.webp 300w, https:\/\/fondationdesfemmes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/02\/plaidoyer-observatoire-emancipation-768x562.webp 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8e3455e e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"8e3455e